GOLDEN FRIENDS said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 15.67% to NT$181,032,000 from NT$214,660,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            181,032          214,660    
YOY%             -15.67%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            803,462          775,193    
YOY%              3.65%  
=================================================================
 